text: This is a wonderful place of worship where prayers are answered. This church people are loving and caring. I am mesmerized and astonished by the hospitality given to me.

Beautifully celebrated the birth of christ at church as a multi lingual worship session. With brothers n sisters from nepal, srilanka, india, africa, malaysia, singapore n more. JesusChrist-The reason for the Season.
Another church building that appears symmetrical on both sides. When I chanced upon this church building, my first thought was, 'Life's Stopover'.
Such a beautiful church filled with beautiful people. Heaven will be like that filled with people from all over the world
New address is 432a serangoon road..opposite perumal temple
